<text xml:lang="ta" type="edition">
  <body>
    <div rend="parallel">
      <lg xml:id="TVM3.6.5">
<l>tiriyuṅ kāṟṟō ṭakalvi cumpu tiṇinta maṇkiṭan takaṭa</l>
<l>leriyun tīyō ṭirucu ṭarteyva maṟṟu maṟṟu muṟṟumāy</l>
<l>kariya mēṉiyaṉ ceyya tāmaraik kaṇṇaṉ kaṇṇaṉviṇ ṇōriṟai</l>
<l>curiyum palkaruṅ kuñci yeṅkaḷ cuṭarmuṭi yaṇṇa ṟōṟṟamē</l>
      </lg>
      <lg xml:lang="en">
<l>Being, along with the wandering wind, the wide sky, the firm earth, the lying sea,</l>
<l>along with the flaming fire the two lights, the gods, other things and other things and all,</l>
<l>is the appearance of our majesty with the glowing crown with much curly black hair,</l>
<l>the lord of the celestials, Kṛṣṇa, the one with red lotus eyes, with a black body.</l>
      </lg>
    </div>
  </body>
</text>
